{"tid":416793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ插沙跪求]有冇何君堯自認英國唔係執業律師既片","createTime":"2017-09-28T05:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T04:17:56.000Z","uid":47359,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"647aee73975f4a2c80cad289b35c49f3415601ee","tid":416793,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:37:30.000Z","msg":"我同另一位巴打聽日會去icac<br />\n想準備多啲<br />\n1sra信soft copy<br />\n2選舉單張hard copy<br />\n仲有冇?"},{"pid":"49a3ffa1c82d60eae1af09f862711a92077ce92c","tid":416793,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ecdaa3a55303034a375e7532fefa715a497e90","tid":416793,"uid":68426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:49:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">推</span>"},{"pid":"83c02f5437d29eaa279ba62ac8ee1576a9c580ad","tid":416793,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cfa67be67c2fc812b045e1ad291d7c8d4b4e99a","tid":416793,"uid":20816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170924/57248542\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170924%2F57248542&d=iSYwik3gVh0G1Y9y2f78fWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=4e024874\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170924%2F57248542&h=a4792e21\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170924/57248542</a><br />\n<br />\n被踢爆無執業即鬼祟改網頁 何君堯涉虛報資歷：手民之誤<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被踢爆無執業即鬼祟改網頁 何君堯涉虛報資歷：手民之誤<br />\n<br />\n 何去年參選立法會時在競選宣傳單張上，列明專業資格是「新加坡和英國及威爾斯執業律師」，被質疑在選舉中虛報資歷。<br />\n何去年參選立法會時在競選宣傳單張上，列明專業資格是「新加坡和英國及威爾斯執業律師」，被質疑在選舉中虛報資歷。<br />\n 現時何的律師樓網頁已修改(左圖)，但立法會網頁上(右圖)仍列明「於1995年成為新加坡執業律師」、「於1995年成為英格蘭及威爾斯執業律師」。<br />\n現時何的律師樓網頁已修改(左圖)，但立法會網頁上(右圖)仍列明「於1995年成為新加坡執業律師」、「於1995年成為英格蘭及威爾斯執業律師」。<br />\n【新增動新聞】<br />\n在選舉宣傳單張自稱「新加坡和英國及威爾斯執業律師」的立法會議員何君堯，繼被揭沒有在英國執業後，再被踢爆在新加坡亦可能只有註冊但無執業，涉虛報資歷誤導選民。何昨短訊回覆傳媒聲稱在新加坡有執業資格但沒有執業，更悄悄修改其所屬的律師樓網頁資料，改為僅是獲英國及新加坡的「執業律師資格」。《星島日報》今報道，何昨回覆查詢時指，律師樓網頁之前的中文版本只是「手民之誤，漏了資格兩字」，又稱已「馬上修正」，對於被指涉誤導選民，何向該報回覆堅持自己沒有誤導。<br />\n<br />\n現時何的律師樓網頁已修改為「於一九九五年獲得新加坡執業律師資格」及「於一九九七年獲得英格蘭及威爾斯執業律師資格」。不過立法會網頁上仍列明他「於1995年成為新加坡執業律師」、「於1995年成為英格蘭及威爾斯執業律師」。<br />\n被指為「西環新契仔」的何去年參選立法會時卻在競選宣傳單張上，列明自己的專業資格是「新加坡和英國及威爾斯執業律師」，被質疑在選舉中虛報資歷，有網民認為應剝奪其議員資格。何前晚在facebook回應事件時，斥今次是「黃色恐怖」，但他無畏無懼，形容「黃毒用文攻武嚇，要你閉嘴」。他昨貼上新加坡最高法院頒授的律師資格證書，最初未有交代是否正在執業，隨後才以短訊回覆《明報》指自己在新加坡有執業資格但沒有執業。<br />\n香港大學法律學院副教授戴耀廷昨在facebook貼出，《選舉（舞弊及非法行為）條例》第26條，有關發佈關於候選人的虛假或具誤導性的陳述的非法行為條文，違例者最高可罰款20萬元及監禁3年。"},{"pid":"b7236eba4b25776068e6121bae98e66304843a68","tid":416793,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:05:43.000Z","msg":"認真po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c1ba16283412b3907245f48326c28aaf41bfd3","tid":416793,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:20:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235c8d9b558d56726c4da8de0a79ea5bec4160a6","tid":416793,"uid":8411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:22:39.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"41125ef47ef5ef5118ddd991d51e795b98f25354","tid":416793,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:23:09.000Z","msg":"樓主加油，唔好俾佢停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d51e54fe2e7e0028ea5503496e8fca0556366f","tid":416793,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:29:59.000Z","msg":"加油！"},{"pid":"9e08d65be6219832a4f20baf528a4e32c2dc936b","tid":416793,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:30:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1820d9733705329629dab114c4daf0e51d0722c4","tid":416793,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"345406b168693dd56e4a49a2eb7a510192ec2961","tid":416793,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:01:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b5ec0581d1d57ce8a97576b7ae582963695f79be","tid":416793,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:04:35.000Z","msg":"請先受我一拜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794c0abea36f52b7dc293f457a99adf076695b44","tid":416793,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:05:21.000Z","msg":"正啊喂"},{"pid":"0f41e3827f11ce366cd9c729589f377ff82dd0a3","tid":416793,"uid":47359,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:05:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">忙碌既巴打請打老廉投訴熱線<br />\n25266366</span></span>"},{"pid":"f9d1ad1f7e99f864ddf6f58d8a57dbfae094465a","tid":416793,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d13611a95c02c8e1c344acf7e72a99f79388db","tid":416793,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:16:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b04dafc014f0f40607cac479687e3ef368e85480","tid":416793,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"巴打好波"},{"pid":"0220204164c771004285ea0b